-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
						
									DYNAMODB STREAMS
									----------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Time-ordered sequence of item level modification (insert,update,delete)
* Logs are encrypted at rest and store for 24 hours
* Accessed using dedicated endpoint
* By default the primary key is recorded
* Before and after image can be captured
* Events are recorded in near real-time
* Application can take actions based on contents
* Event source for lambda 
* Lambda polls the dynamoDB stream
* Execute lambda code based on dynamoDb stream event
